title: Carb Smart Pork Ragout Bake with Eggplant and Basil
description: You won't miss the pasta in this flavour-packed pork ragout bake! Layers of seasoned pork, juicy eggplant and gooey cheese await with every bite! Ricotta and mozzarella form the perfect golden cheesy topping – bellissimo!

